{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerWhatsappNumber:","symbolKind":"method","title":"registerWhatsappNumber:"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"number"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"number","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number in E.164 international format.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates a WhatsApp number with the current device for WhatsApp Business API"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"messaging campaigns. This enables rich messaging with images, documents, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interactive buttons through WhatsApp."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number must be in E.164 international format:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Start with ‘+’ followed by country code"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No spaces, dashes, or parentheses"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a valid WhatsApp-enabled number"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Register WhatsApp during communication preferences setup:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class CommunicationPreferencesManager {","","    struct Preferences {","        var pushEnabled: Bool","        var smsEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappNumber: String?","    }","","    func savePreferences(_ preferences: Preferences) {","        \/\/ Register WhatsApp if user opted in and provided number","        if preferences.whatsappEnabled, let number = preferences.whatsappNumber {","            let normalizedNumber = normalizePhoneNumber(number)","            Pushwoosh.configure.registerWhatsappNumber(normalizedNumber)","        }","","        \/\/ Update channel preferences tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"channel_push\": preferences.pushEnabled,","            \"channel_sms\": preferences.smsEnabled,","            \"channel_whatsapp\": preferences.whatsappEnabled","        ])","    }","","    private func normalizePhoneNumber(_ phone: String) -> String {","        let digits = phone.filter { $0.isNumber }","        return phone.hasPrefix(\"+\") ? \"+\\(digits)\" : \"+\\(digits)\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerWhatsappNumber:":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerWhatsappNumber:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging."}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:","type":"topic","title":"registerWhatsappNumber:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}